testlink.api.java.client.tc.autoexec
Class EmptyExecutor

java.lang.Object
  testlink.api.java.client.tc.autoexec.EmptyExecutor
All Implemented Interfaces:
TestCaseExecutor
Direct Known Subclasses:
RandomTestResultExecutor, RemoteClientExecutor
public class EmptyExecutor
extends java.lang.Object
implements TestCaseExecutor

This class can be used to write custom excutors by overriding the execute method. It can also be used for testing since it will return an execution of failed if the default constructor is used or the result provided to the defaultResult constructor.

Author:
Daniel Padilla
